      <pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 07:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <category>agent-sdk-ts-changelog</category>
      <description>- Deprecated the unstable V2 session API (unstablev2createSession / unstablev2resumeSession / unstablev2prompt) — use query() instead
- Deprecated passing &apos;Skill&apos; in allowedTools — use the skills option instead
- Updated to parity with Claude Code v2.1.133</description>
